Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:55.44,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}A Mountain Hike - The End of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:46.47,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:49.26,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:07.74,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:13.71,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:22.55,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:26.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.37,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:32.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:33.98,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:39.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:45.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:52.20,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:57.95,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:02.59,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:44.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:52.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:54.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Main armament, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance, 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell. HE round.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shell loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Signal the forces to our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit destroyed. Take up our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, it's Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My. Then let's have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back on your feet again, aren't you, Shuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:06.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely healed, but she just won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this place is just wonderful, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:13.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she run around like that when it's so hot out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:27.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's your mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:56.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And one for you, Noël. From the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His first name is Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His last name is Fessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Common names in the Sept region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Mr. Fessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful that you have friends from so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:32.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Noël! I almost believed you for a second there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Klaus something for the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are our orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:36.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:48.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you for everything every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:50.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll take care of the place while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck out there, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Y- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on a field trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound great, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A field trip? Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:44.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just walking would be a bit boring, so let's play a little game while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, all along the southern edges of Seize,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, the border between Seize and Nomansland,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,there are surveillance devices from the ancient past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:02.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of these, three are due for regular maintenance checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:06.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to look at them during our field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission's not even disguised!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just your normal field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything even if they were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:20.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noctur-Type Surveillance Devices are a complete black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Analysis is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what he meant by "Good luck out there."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But just walking is putting time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, you three
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,will be carrying those on your backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:49.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. To carry something like this, you have to put your body weight forward and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Botcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:12.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all such good children. You've met all of our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:18.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! When you're lifting a heavy pack, first you lie back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:27.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then once the full weight of the pack is on your back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:43.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your yappin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:57.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Now then. Filicia and I will go ahead to the goal point on your map and wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:01.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If at any point you don't think you can go on, blow your bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:11.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are wild animals on this mountain. Should you encounter one, in order to handle the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I authorize the use of firearms,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun now, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,March!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:05.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too heavy! Too heavy! Too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it gets heavier every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, how much farther?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:40.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In working order. No abnormalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on. That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:27.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that I thought about this machine protecting the town all alone, all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Noël, where's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Th- Th- That mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:05.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:10.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone do something about these packs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:47.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. The Commander and Rio both hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:57.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say something, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:13:01.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:19.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so refreshing! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,R&R!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:58.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what anyone says, we are getting R&R! Because I say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:12.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody else was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:34.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:41.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, this is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:52.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a field trip. We have to make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget about those stupidly-heavy sacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is training!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But Filicia said-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, are you blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's black-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Blacker than coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But her hair is blonde and her skin is so white and she's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's good about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:23.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are talking about a different Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:27.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Someone do something about this pair of airheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, time for food! Time for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:38.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll dry soon with this sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our food is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was a boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:55.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in my village, they dug up our fields pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:59.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a lot of food during the summer, so they usually wouldn't come near.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a bigger problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The compass is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:12.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's okay to leave those packs there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first priority should be reaching the goal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we headed in the right direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first device was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The river was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:27.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The second device is at the summit of the mountain we're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just need to head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! No matter what-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's anything we can eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:52.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sweet, a little sour, and just delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't climb up that. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:15.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Major Klaus once crossed a desert in a tank without food or water for three days and took down an enemy fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They call him the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an amazing person...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Klaus is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bayberries...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:01.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:16.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just where is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:20.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten pretty dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to get our bearings after every turn, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:26.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "probably"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a compass, I can't be completely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:36.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what? We walked all this way for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:42.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If the compass was that important, you should have kept it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:47.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not start fighting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for playing in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:19:02.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always spacing out and smiling like an idiot! That's why we're in this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:20.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Well, it looks like they'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:13.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you! I got you, so get off me! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomansland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:43.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of the world we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:53.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I apologize! We were unable to complete the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:56.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What mission are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All we wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was for you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:10.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the signatures of those who came before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:14.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Every maiden of the fortress has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:20.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And has seen this. The end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our past, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk just a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:36.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing they left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:21:59.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like coming back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:19.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:36.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was worth the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:14.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,405)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Kanata's Day Off - Hair Ties
